        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Markdown-Cheat-Sheet-for-Hexo-Blogging"><a href="#Markdown-Cheat-Sheet-for-Hexo-Blogging" class="headerlink" title="Markdown Cheat Sheet for Hexo Blogging"></a>Markdown Cheat Sheet for Hexo Blogging</h1><h2 id="Article-Header-Hexo-specific"><a href="#Article-Header-Hexo-specific" class="headerlink" title="Article Header (Hexo-specific)"></a>Article Header (Hexo-specific)</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">***</span><br><span class="line">title: Your Post Title</span><br><span class="line">date: 2025-11-03 14:00:00</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- Hexo</span><br><span class="line">- Markdown</span><br><span class="line">categories: Blog</span><br><span class="line">***</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="Headings"><a href="#Headings" class="headerlink" title="Headings"></a>Headings</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># Heading level 1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## Heading level 2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">### Heading level 3</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#### Heading level 4</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">##### Heading level 5</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">###### Heading level 6</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Heading-level-1"><a href="#Heading-level-1" class="headerlink" title="Heading level 1"></a>Heading level 1</h1><h2 id="Heading-level-2"><a href="#Heading-level-2" class="headerlink" title="Heading level 2"></a>Heading level 2</h2><h3 id="Heading-level-3"><a href="#Heading-level-3" class="headerlink" title="Heading level 3"></a>Heading level 3</h3><h4 id="Heading-level-4"><a href="#Heading-level-4" class="headerlink" title="Heading level 4"></a>Heading level 4</h4><h5 id="Heading-level-5"><a href="#Heading-level-5" class="headerlink" title="Heading level 5"></a>Heading level 5</h5><h6 id="Heading-level-6"><a href="#Heading-level-6" class="headerlink" title="Heading level 6"></a>Heading level 6</h6><hr><h2 id="Paragraphs-and-Line-Breaks"><a href="#Paragraphs-and-Line-Breaks" class="headerlink" title="Paragraphs and Line Breaks"></a>Paragraphs and Line Breaks</h2><p>Separate paragraphs with a blank line.<br>Add two spaces at the end of a line for a line break.</p><hr><h2 id="Text-Styles"><a href="#Text-Styles" class="headerlink" title="Text Styles"></a>Text Styles</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">*Italic* or _Italic_</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">**Bold** or __Bold__</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">***Bold and Italic***</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">~~Strikethrough~~</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;u&gt;Underline (HTML tags can be used)&lt;/u&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>Italic</em> or <em>Italic</em></p><p><strong>Bold</strong> or <strong>Bold</strong></p><p><em><strong>Bold and Italic</strong></em></p><p><del>Strikethrough</del></p><p><u>Underline (HTML tags can be used)</u></p><hr><h2 id="Lists"><a href="#Lists" class="headerlink" title="Lists"></a>Lists</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- Unordered list item</span><br><span class="line">- Another item</span><br><span class="line">    - Nested item</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">1. Ordered list item</span><br><span class="line">2. Second item</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>Unordered list item</li><li>Another item<ul><li>Nested item</li></ul></li></ul><ol><li>Ordered list item</li><li>Second item</li></ol><hr><h2 id="Blockquotes"><a href="#Blockquotes" class="headerlink" title="Blockquotes"></a>Blockquotes</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt; This is a blockquote.</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; Nested blockquote.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>This is a blockquote.</p><blockquote><p>Nested blockquote.</p></blockquote></blockquote><hr><h2 id="Code"><a href="#Code" class="headerlink" title="Code"></a>Code</h2><p>Inline code:  </p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">`inline code`</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>inline code</code></p><p>Code block:  </p><pre><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Multi-line code block</span><br><span class="line">Multiple lines supported</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></pre><p>Syntax highlighting (example for Python):  </p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">```python</span><br><span class="line">print(&quot;Hello Hexo!&quot;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">```python</span><br><span class="line">print(&quot;Hello Hexo!&quot;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="Links-and-Images"><a href="#Links-and-Images" class="headerlink" title="Links and Images"></a>Links and Images</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[Link text](https://example.com)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Local image example:  </p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="Tables"><a href="#Tables" class="headerlink" title="Tables"></a>Tables</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">| Column 1 | Column 2 |</span><br><span class="line">| :-- | :-- |</span><br><span class="line">| ContentA | ContentB |</span><br><span class="line">| ContentC | ContentD |</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="left">Column 1</th><th align="left">Column 2</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">ContentA</td><td align="left">ContentB</td></tr><tr><td align="left">ContentC</td><td align="left">ContentD</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="Horizontal-Rules"><a href="#Horizontal-Rules" class="headerlink" title="Horizontal Rules"></a>Horizontal Rules</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">***</span><br><span class="line">***</span><br><span class="line">___</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><hr><hr><hr><h2 id="Escaping-Characters"><a href="#Escaping-Characters" class="headerlink" title="Escaping Characters"></a>Escaping Characters</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">\*This asterisk will display as a literal character*</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>*This asterisk will display as a literal character*</p><hr><h2 id="Task-Lists"><a href="#Task-Lists" class="headerlink" title="Task Lists"></a>Task Lists</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- [x] Completed task</span><br><span class="line">- [ ] Incomplete task</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> Completed task</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Incomplete task</li></ul><hr><h2 id="Comments-Invisible-in-output"><a href="#Comments-Invisible-in-output" class="headerlink" title="Comments (Invisible in output)"></a>Comments (Invisible in output)</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- This is a comment --&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><!-- This is a comment --><hr><h2 id="Inline-HTML"><a href="#Inline-HTML" class="headerlink" title="Inline HTML"></a>Inline HTML</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;span style=&quot;color: red;&quot;&gt;Red Text&lt;/span&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="Hexo-Extended-Syntax"><a href="#Hexo-Extended-Syntax" class="headerlink" title="Hexo Extended Syntax"></a>Hexo Extended Syntax</h2><ul><li>Mathematics (if supported by theme&#x2F;plugins):</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">\$ E = mc^2 \$</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>$ E &#x3D; mc^2 $</p><ul><li>Table of Contents:</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[TOC]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>[TOC]</p><ul><li>Footnotes (if supported):</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Here is a footnote reference.[^1]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;span style=&quot;display:none&quot;&gt;[^2][^3][^4][^5][^6][^7][^8][^9]&lt;/span&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;div align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;⁂&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[^1]: https://www.markdownguide.org/basic-syntax/</span><br><span class="line">[^2]: https://www.markdownguide.org/cheat-sheet/</span><br><span class="line">[^3]: https://gist.github.com/cuonggt/9b7d08a597b167299f0d</span><br><span class="line">[^4]: https://markdownlivepreview.dev/cheatsheet</span><br><span class="line">[^5]: https://dev.to/mahbubumithu/a-complete-markdown-tutorial-from-basics-to-advanced-41nb</span><br><span class="line">[^6]: https://www.markdownguide.org/extended-syntax/</span><br><span class="line">[^7]: https://www.markdownguide.org</span><br><span class="line">[^8]: https://github.com/adam-p/markdown-here/wiki/markdown-cheatsheet</span><br><span class="line">[^9]: https://commonmark.org/help/```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><span style="display:none"><a href="https://gist.github.com/cuonggt/9b7d08a597b167299f0d">^2</a><a href="https://dev.to/mahbubumithu/a-complete-markdown-tutorial-from-basics-to-advanced-41nb">^4</a><a href="https://www.markdownguide.org/">^6</a><a href="https://commonmark.org/help/">^8</a></span></p><div align="center">⁂</div>]]></content>
      
      
      
